<div class="col-lg-8 col-12 mx-auto">
	<p><strong>Why do I need a studio policy?</strong></p>
	<p>An effective studio policy is one of the most important tools a piano teacher has for creating a private studio. Designing your piano studio policy is a great way to go through all of the important aspects of your studio, learn and decide how you will handle the tricky situations that are likely to come by.</p>
